attributes.description: The "TYCHON Endpoint Browser" dashboard provides host visualization data for a single endpoint at a time. The dashboard is a set of several individual views broken down by tabs near the top of the screen. The TYCHON Endpoint Browser â€“ Host Information view displays overall Operating System data and summary information from its subordinate datasets (disks, drives, vulnerabilities, benchmarks, etc.).
